   "source": [
    "# load important dependencies \n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import sympy as sp\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "tags": []
   },
   "source": [
    "# 无约束优化（optimtool.unconstrain）\n",
    "```python\n",
    "import optimtool.unconstrain as ou\n",
    "ou.[方法名].[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点])\n",
    "```\n",
    "$$\n",
    "f(x)=\\sum_{i=1}^{n/2}(-13+x_{2i-1}+((5-x_{2i})x_{2i}-2)x_{2i})^2+(-29+x_{2i-1}+((x_{2i}+1)x_{2i}-14)x_{2i})^2, x_0=[0.5, -2, 0.5, -2, ..., 0.5, -2].\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import optimtool.unconstrain as ou\n",
    "x = sp.symbols(\"x1:5\")\n",
    "f = (-13 + x[0] + ((5 - x[1])*x[1] - 2)*x[1])**2 + \\\n",
    "    (-29 + x[0] + ((x[1] + 1)*x[1] - 14)*x[1])**2 + \\\n",
    "    (-13 + x[2] + ((5 - x[3])*x[3] - 2)*x[3])**2 + \\\n",
    "    (-29 + x[2] + ((x[3] + 1)*x[3] - 14)*x[3])**2\n",
    "x_0 = (1, -1, 1, -1) # Random given"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 梯度下降法（gradient_descent）\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "ou.gradient_descent.[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点])\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "| 方法头                                                                                                                                 | 解释                                   |\n",
    "| ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------ |\n",
    "| solve(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType                                                             | 通过解方程的方式来求解精确步长                      |\n",
    "| steepest(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"wolfe\", epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType                                           | 使用线搜索方法求解非精确步长（默认使用wolfe线搜索）         |\n",
    "| barzilar_borwein(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"Grippo\", c1: float=0.6, beta: float=0.6, alpha: float=1, epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType | 使用Grippo与ZhangHanger提出的非单调线搜索方法更新步长 |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",

     "execution_count": 3,

     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ou.gradient_descent.barzilar_borwein(f, x, x_0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "attachments": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 牛顿法（newton)\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "ou.newton.[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点])\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "| 方法头                                                                                             | 解释                                |\n",
    "| ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------- |\n",
    "| classic(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType                        | 通过直接对目标函数二阶导矩阵（海瑟矩阵）进行求逆来获取下一步的步长 |\n",
    "| modified(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"wolfe\", epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType | 修正当前海瑟矩阵保证其正定性（目前只接入了一种修正方法）      |\n",
    "| CG(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"wolfe\", epsilon: float=1e-6, k: int=0) -> OutputType              | 采用牛顿-共轭梯度法求解梯度（非精确牛顿法的一种）         |"
   ]
  },

    "## 拟牛顿法（newton_quasi）\n",

    "| dfp(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"wolfe\", epsilon: float=1e-4, k: int=0) -> OutputType    | DFP方法更新海瑟矩阵     |\n",
    "| L_BFGS(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"wolfe\", m: float=6, epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType | 双循环方法更新BFGS海瑟矩阵 |\n"

    "## 非线性最小二乘法（nonlinear_least_square）\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "ou.nonlinear_least_square.[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点])\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "| 方法头                                                                                                                                                  | 解释                         |\n",
    "| ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------- |\n",
    "| gauss_newton(funcr: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"wolfe\", epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType                                                        | 高斯-牛顿提出的方法框架，包括OR分解等操作     |\n",
    "| levenberg_marquardt(funcr: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, lamk: float=1, eta: float=0.2, p1: float=0.4, p2: float=0.9, gamma1: float=0.7, gamma2: float=1.3, epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType | Levenberg Marquardt提出的方法框架 |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",

       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },

     },

    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "(array([1.00000000e+00, 6.08502493e-21]), 6)"
      ]

     "execution_count": 6,

     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "r1, r2, x1, x2 = sp.symbols(\"r1 r2 x1 x2\")\n",
    "r1 = x1**3 - 2*x2**2 - 1\n",
    "r2 = 2*x1 + x2 - 2\n",
    "ou.nonlinear_least_square.gauss_newton((r1, r2), (x1, x2), (1, 1))"
   ]
